Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 安谢尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把他带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你说的那个孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我希望你能赐血给他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我分些血给他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所 所罗门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被选上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\bord0\fad(1500,0)}直至疯狂
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.40,0:02:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\alpha&H3f\bord1\fad(1500,0)}{\3c&HB4FE43&}直至疯狂
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.60,0:02:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\alpha&H8f\bord3\fad(1500,0)}{\3c&HB4FE43&}直至疯狂
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\alpha&Hbf\bord5\fad(1500,0)}{\3c&HB4FE43&}直至疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从与小夜在柯文特皇家剧院一战的次日起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原订计划就取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的公演都取消了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有最后一场公演的网上订票还在实施
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为封锁区域渐渐被开放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们终于可以专心搞公演了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次调查的那个设施也已是空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉娅那边有联络吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 明明是哈比亚的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是哈比亚的生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯不在就没有人陪小孩子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他和莫尼克去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔一次也可以转换一下气氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了 感觉像是硬要你陪我出来买东西似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比亚也因为是第一次给自己开生日会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以特别兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有这么多人给她庆祝应该很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 生日会挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想小夜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在想她现在在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫尼克 等我一会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌之女神的公演终止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会治好的 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你受了很重的伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是哈比亚五岁的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家打算一起搞聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会做丰盛的菜肴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得热热闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是那孩子第一次办生日会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望庆祝的人越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 小夜小姐也请来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定请来参加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家的准备还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可千万要避免像上次那样的失态了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔加农先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZONE Z运来的行李出现了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 集装箱被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 是宴会的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事我们会处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要按照计划行事即可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌之女神平安到达克利斯切那岛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔似乎擅自带了尸体兵团出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是...小夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对卡尔而言小夜既是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上也是他的生存价值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果对卡尔而言小夜是生存价值的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更是如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是杀不掉小夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红盾已经不是什么威胁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夜不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么办 要去救卡尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用我说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在德国时你做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真是个残酷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐 哈比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然联络我们还以为是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是小孩子的生日会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可没准备什么礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没告诉你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱唱歌就好了 重要的是心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,happy br..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比亚 你久等的蛋糕来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一个人吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 点蜡烛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还叫了什么其他人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 是小熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日时收到礼物固然好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过能一起庆祝的话会更令人高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:08:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有些事想和你好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这孩子说你是不是孤身一人啊 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都为你能来而高兴著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在冲绳的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸有一次突然做了蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 其实是想给你过生日的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是蛋糕没做成就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过作为弥补却让我大吃了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段时光 就像是做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们究竟为了什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着哈比亚和那哈比 我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾以那样的表情笑过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经 无法回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我是翼手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸今天晚上能见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的你将自己交托于近乎疯狂的纯粹的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏了所有能动的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人也好禽兽也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无差别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的你实在太美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说就是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与歌之女神相同 给世界带来混沌与破坏的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我看一眼吧 你那姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今宵与我共舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很疯狂 而你也很疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配得上我和你的舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让人阻碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你共舞的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我们来守着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点哦 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜的骑士 感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴啊  小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里就只有我和你两人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在互相厮杀的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你都只想着对方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只属于两人的美丽时光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让任何人妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 只想着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想着如何杀掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是这刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲爱的小夜 现在就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卡尔变成骑士的时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他并非自愿而成为骑士的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据格雷戈里的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌之女神的血可以改变一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有个体差异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是蒙古人种却十分适合这种血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只能从亚洲一带获得实验素材的时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔被选中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是delta计划就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在俄罗斯播种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在德国发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在越南结果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此所需要的就是卡尔的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是需要拥有身为骑士的不死体质的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验材料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那家伙却向歌之女神要求爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本是不可能得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只丑陋的手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了杀掉你 我接受了安谢尔的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安谢尔在越南找到我后这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果作为实验材料的话 就让你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我的命运早就决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从成为骑士的一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体就被切碎 再不断拼接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了知道骑士究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的希望就只有歌之女神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这身体里留着的歌之女神的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是作为骑士的羁绊的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够接受歌之女神的爱 才是我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 歌之女神离开了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于明白到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够理解我的就只有身为敌人的 小夜你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经只剩下你一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快把那家伙给...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至被家人背叛了的你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为他人的愿望而降生于世的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要像这样把你的颈部咬碎喝干你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被人期望的同类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于我们两人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在这种地方输掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有许多必须要守护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的卡尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果硬拔出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内脏会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话你也不会安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 回到你们的睡床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我一直很羡慕卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么纯粹 一直按自己的想法而活的他的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那却是我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是太过孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 对被孤立的你产生了同伴意识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你和卡尔是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有许多一直看护着你的伙伴在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你却自己选择孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是直到你说出口为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔连这件事都没察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有察觉到身处孤独之中 逃避著一切不便事端的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有察觉到还有一直看护着他的我在...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周后 歌之女神似乎会去库利斯切那岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信我请你自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要告诉我这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我也很孤独吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 你要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须打倒歌之女神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你一个人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们大家的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...想保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说这个世界上有能称为敌人的存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图加害我所爱的歌之女神的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要尽全力排除你们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将翼手的世界扩大的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多少人都无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 BLOOD+
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决战之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命 献给歌之女神
